{"tid":1596490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"遭老牌旅遊公司破產殃及 中資財團損失10億或考慮拋售狼隊","createTime":"2019-09-26T13:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T15:24:58.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6298ddcf68e5d8eb84a391d03cf83e9fca0f6e","tid":1596490,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"英國老牌旅遊公司托馬斯庫克日前宣告破產，狼隊的中資控股公司覆星集團因此損失10億英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n狼隊的母公司中國覆星集團被披露是托馬斯-庫克的最大單一股東，他們從2015年開始收購這家公司的股份，至今已持有18%的股份，投資金額超過10億英鎊。<br />\n消息曝光後，狼隊官方堅稱，托馬斯-庫克的倒台所帶來的所有損失都不會對莫利紐斯球場產生影響。但也有消息稱，覆星集團正積極尋求在其他產業的投資，因此願意出售至多20%的俱樂部股份套現。<br />\n覆星集團三年前以4500萬鎊收購狼隊，不僅幫助球隊成功升入英超，還在上賽季取得英超第七名並獲得本賽季歐聯杯的參賽資格。可是新賽季狼隊的表現不盡如人意，聯賽至今仍一勝難求。"},{"pid":"08297575413f8fd7539fc4a4fc0f338fac8b3cca","tid":1596490,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"戴狗點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293d41ab7b8ae33d5daced837f3e8bdcb1a63384","tid":1596490,"uid":6736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"復星邊會咁窮 不過支那tsun都算黑氣石 快啲入中國國家隊武磊即刻斷腳都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c422ce6685061d8ac9e4b77999a8364f9299398","tid":1596490,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08297575413f8fd7539fc4a4fc0f338fac8b3cca","tid":1596490,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"戴狗點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/